Read GP OOH Consultations extract

Source: R/read_extract_ooh_consultations.R
read_extract_ooh_consultations.Rd

Read GP OOH Consultations extract

Usage

read_extract_ooh_consultations(
  year,
  file_path = get_boxi_extract_path(year = year, type = "gp_ooh-c")
)

Arguments

year

Financial year for the BOXI extract.

file_path

BOXI extract location

Value

a tibble with OOH Consultations extract data
